name: Daily Visitors
query:
select 
    `tabDaily Visitors`.name1  as "إسم الزائر::200" ,
    `tabDaily Visit`.no_old as "رقم البطاقة::150",
    `tabDaily Visit`.visit_type as "نوع الزيارة::100",
    `tabDaily Visit`.visit_depart as " جهة الزيارة::150",
    `tabDaily Visit`.visit_date as "تاريخ الزيارة::100" ,
    `tabDaily Visit`.time as "وقت الزياره::100",
    `tabDaily Visit`.visit_reason as " سبب الزيارة ::100"


    
from
        `tabDaily Visit` 
JOIN    
    `tabDaily Visitors` ON `tabDaily Visitors`.name = `tabDaily Visit`.visitors


where
    `tabDaily Visit`.visit_date >= %(from_date)s and `tabDaily Visit`.visit_date <= %(to_date)s
